  Sian-siN koh kong2, ¡§Li2 e7-ki3-tit Ia5-sou chit-tiap8 ti7 lau5-teng2 kap li2, goa2, put-chi2 kin7. Lan2 tai7-ke kap i kong2-oe7, i chit8-ku3 chit8-ku3 long2 thiaN-kiN3 lah, lian5 lan2 teh thou2-khui3 e5 siaN iah kau3 i hi7-khang-lai7; koh-chai3 lan2 e5 sim hiong3 ti7 to2-ui7, lan2 taN m7-sai2 tai7-seng kap Chu2 kong2 siaN2-mih8, chong2-tioh8 thiaN Chu2 tui3 lan2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7.¡¨ Chiu7 hian-khui Seng3-keng thak8 nng7 chat, teh thak8--e5 si7 Chu2 kong2, ¡§Lin2 long2 lai5, goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2, lin2 e5 choe7-ok koan3-boan2, i-e5 sek-ti7 tang7 chhin-chhiuN7 chhiah, chhim chhin-chhiuN7 ang5; goa2 tek-khak hou7 i kau3 chin7 peh8 chheng-khi3, chhin-chhiuN7 mi5 chhin-chhiuN7 seh.(I2-sai3-a2 1:18) 
